data.description: Welcome to this Beautiful two-story home. This floor plan includes a upstairs loft that's perfect for working from home or an extra living space. The open kitchen features a gas stove, lots of counter-space, a spacious corner pantry, tons of cabinet space, and a island great for enteraining. The kitchen opens to the living room great for family gatherings. Home to 1625 sq ft 3 bedroom 2.5 Bathroom very well maintained home built in 2019. The backyard has a sprinkler system and is just as spacious with the possibilities being endless! Definitely a Must see! This home offers a short commute to Randolph Air Force Base and Fort Sam Houston, 1604, and major shopping centers. Resort-style amenities including pool, splash pad, playground, and sports court are available to the next homeowner!
